member.name: OLECMDF
member.summary: Specifies the type of support provided by an object for the command specified in an structure.

member.name: OLECMDF.OLECMDF_SUPPORTED
member.summary: The command is supported by this object.

member.name: OLECMDF.OLECMDF_ENABLED
member.summary: The command is available and enabled.

member.name: OLECMDF.OLECMDF_LATCHED
member.summary: The command is an on-off toggle and is currently on.

member.name: OLECMDF.OLECMDF_DEFHIDEONCTXTMENU
member.summary: The command is hidden on the context menu.
